data.description: Great curb appeal on this Paras rancher in beautiful Trickle Creek. This is the Camille plan with 2017 sq.ft. Has 3 bedrooms, 2 baths and a den. All the Paras quality with stained kitchen cabinets, quartz countertops, wood floors through the entryway, kitchen, dinning area and great room area. Refrigerator included.  Primary bedroom has large walk-in mud set shower, double vanity with quartz tops and large walk-in closets. Lovely floor to ceiling fireplace with wood mantle and built in cabinets. Has nice covered deck. This home will be fully landscaped and includes fence in the backyard.
